xml.panel_title: Please, pay attention to the information below!
xml.panel_text: Please, note, installing new layout via Installer panel will overwrite the existing options and Revolution sliders. You can install only the layout content with WordPress importer from themeforest theme archive>Mainfiles>import>layout>layout.zip to get the needed page without damaging the existing content. Make sure that all plugins, provided with the theme, are installed. You can check that in “Appearance>Install plugins” section.
